flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Daily scheduled ingest (overnight batch) plus event-driven ingest for recalls/campaigns or field failure signals.]
  A --> N1[Stream: STREAMS - Consolidate nightly transactional and master data from SAP S/4HANA and dealer portals using STREAMS]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Run SKU-level demand and lifecycle-aware forecasting with Cortex Auto Forecast, including recall/campaign uplift and EV segment modeling]
  N2 --> N3{PB: Process Builder - Apply replenishment rules, allocation logic and business policies in Process Builder; surface recommendations and exceptions via CWB Lifecycle where thresholds exceeded}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[PB: Remote Functions - Execute approved replenishment orders and allocation writes to SAP S/4HANA via Remote Functions and trigger procurement workflows]
  N4 --> N5[PB: UI Screens - Notify planners and stakeholders of recommendations, exceptions, and campaign-driven changes through UI Screens and Notifications]
  N5 --> N6[PB: Cortex Monitoring - Monitor forecast accuracy, exception patterns, and inventory KPIs via Cortex Monitoring and dashboards; feed learnings back into rules and models]
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Continuous alignment of inventory and procurement with demand signals: lower working capital and excess/obsolete parts, improved on-time parts availability, reduced emergency procurements for recalls/campaigns, and more accurate COGS allocation across the service parts network.]
  N3 -->|Forecast variance or model confidence...| B1[Route to CWB Lifecycle for planner review and trigger Data Science subprocess for additional feature enrichment]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Human-in-the-loop decision or model retrain request; prevent auto-apply to avoid misallocation]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Active recall/campaign with predicted...| B2[Override normal prioritization rules in Process Builder to allocate supply to recall SKUs and accelerate procurement; notify logistics & field teams]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Rapid reallocation of inventory to support campaign, minimizing service disruption]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Supplier constraint or inbound delay ...| B3[Trigger alternative sourcing Remote Function, create backorder plan, and escalate via Notification to procurement team]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Mitigate stockouts through alternate suppliers or prioritized allocation; maintain service levels where possible]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]